    {
      "bookmarkId": "757881_16_737-824",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "737-824",
      "markText": "我的残疾并未对我的科学研究形成严重的障碍。事实上，我猜想在某些方面这反而是财富：我不必去讲课或者去教本科生，而且我也不必参与冗长的耗时的委员会。这样，我能够全身心地投入研究。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757881&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=737&rangeEnd=824",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3a321205b9079b3af3b0c6?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=737&rangeEnd=824"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757881_6_2856-2890",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2856-2890",
      "markText": "当你要面临夭折时，你就意识到生命是值得过的，因为有很多事情等你去做。",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757881&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2856&rangeEnd=2890",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3a321205b9079b3af3b0c6?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2856&rangeEnd=2890"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757881_14_6209-6269",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "6209-6269",
      "markText": "即使在将来发现了某种不同理论，我认为时间旅行将永不可能。如果那是可能的，时到如今，我们早就该备受来自未来的旅客的蹂躏了。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757881&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=6209&rangeEnd=6269",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3a321205b9079b3af3b0c6?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=6209&rangeEnd=6269"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757881_3_521-584",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "521-584",
      "markText": "霍金诞生于1942年1月8日，这天正是伽利略的300年忌日，而牛顿又恰巧诞生于伽利略逝世的那一年，这似乎暗示着霍金一生的使命。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757881&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=521&rangeEnd=584",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3a321205b9079b3af3b0c6?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=521&rangeEnd=584"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757881_6_2285-2356",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2285-2356",
      "markText": "你要么是不费吹灰之力而非常卓越，要么接受自己能力有限而得到第四等。因为用功而得到较好等级被视为一个“灰人”的标志，在牛津词汇中这是最坏的诨名。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757881&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2285&rangeEnd=2356",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3a321205b9079b3af3b0c6?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2285&rangeEnd=2356"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757881_13_3136-3148",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "3136-3148",
      "markText": "效仿是奉承的最真诚形式。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757881&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3136&rangeEnd=3148",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3a321205b9079b3af3b0c6?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=3136&rangeEnd=3148"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757881_4_5599-5625",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5599-5625",
      "markText": "如果你理解宇宙如何运行，在某种程度上，你就控制了它。",
      "totalCount": 104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757881&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5599&rangeEnd=5625",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3a321205b9079b3af3b0c6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5599&rangeEnd=5625"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757881_5_5145-5181",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5145-5181",
      "markText": "对于学物理的，你上哪个学校、结交了哪个人都不重要。只有你做了什么才要紧。",
      "totalCount": 91,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757881&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5145&rangeEnd=5181",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3a321205b9079b3af3b0c6?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5145&rangeEnd=5181"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757881_14_3069-3092",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "3069-3092",
      "markText": "在科学中，寻找问题的正确表述经常是解决它的关键",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757881&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=3069&rangeEnd=3092",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3a321205b9079b3af3b0c6?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=3069&rangeEnd=3092"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757881_16_2648-2700",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "2648-2700",
      "markText": "活着并从事理论物理研究，使我拥有一个美妙的生涯。如果说我曾经为理解宇宙添砖加瓦的话，我会因此而感到快乐。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757881&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2648&rangeEnd=2700",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3a321205b9079b3af3b0c6?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=2648&rangeEnd=2700"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "757881_5_6778-6868",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6778-6868",
      "markText": "现在我是一名数学教授，但自从17岁离开圣奥尔本斯学校起，从未上过正式的数学课。我现在通晓的数学全凭在研究工作中自己汲取。我在剑桥通常指导本科生，只要在课程上比他们提前一周预看即可。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=757881&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6778&rangeEnd=6868",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b3a321205b9079b3af3b0c6?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6778&rangeEnd=6868"
    },
    {
